visitor program mathematics research center skip to main content side content related content stanford university mathematics research center search this site about the mrc visitor program events media & publications contact visitor program home visitor program the mathematic research center has sponsored several long term focused research programs each involving collaborations between mathematicians from stanford and other internationally known scholars the mrc helps maintain a vibrant visitor program each year dozens of prominent mathematicians come to stanford for visits of varying length the visits range from short visits to give a seminar or colloquium on their recent work or visits of two to four weeks for intensive collaborations with stanford faculty summer visits to pursue on going research programs or book projects or long sabbatical visits of a quarter or a year see the current and past visitors for more information on our visitor program please refer to the resources section home about the mrc visitor program resources visitors media & publications events contact footer links sunet login guest login department of mathematics mathematics research center building 380 stanford california 94305 phone 650 725 6284 fax 650 725 4066 stanford university terms of use copyright complaints
